{"tid":1401821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"班前線真係好撚ON9","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T15:27:05.000Z","uid":37901,"like":6,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bb7a5792691e34586336f5faefa3698f3a2db7eb","tid":1401821,"uid":37901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:13:25.000Z","msg":"係啊，講緊你地啊！你後面班和理非ＢＡＣＫ　ＵＰ俾人講兩句帶風向就拋棄你地，你地都仲付出<br />\n你話佢地前線ＯＮ９唔ＯＮ９？<br />\n一個ＰＯＳＴ屌前線無腦有幾千正評？你係前線？你知唔知前線有時資訊真係唔流通？<br />\n好，你可以話，你有講野既自由，你可以俾意見<br />\n但係運動第一日就講明不分化，呢家有義士跳樓死，有人為左咁俾人拉，要坐十碌！<br />\n我地已經無野可以為佢地做，係咪連支持都唔得？意見可以照俾，但係現場做咩決定，佢地堅持要做既，我地都要全力支持，唔分化，唔拋棄！<br />\n<br />\n記住，今次一輸，香港就收皮架啦！唔好拋棄你地口中班無腦前線啦！"},{"pid":"3fbce0033329294baa61ee9b8c0b46cdfd4f1683","tid":1401821,"uid":78186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:15:16.000Z","msg":"我見到都好撚嬲<br />\n大家一家要守撚住網軍"},{"pid":"d83302f6674357d58bcced0f58f859e7d07458c9","tid":1401821,"uid":26813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:15:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">sorry借位宣傳<br />\n幫手推俾前線手足睇！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［前線路障快閃團］簡易快速拆鐵欄攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400592</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"42ad24a59fcdd1b2b4d18806c9ce190c21a00967","tid":1401821,"uid":12426,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:15:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">明顯有狗扮示威者<br />\n引你地留低</span></span>"},{"pid":"138a2797302d5abd8d792a11c5d30964cc229943","tid":1401821,"uid":54774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:16:39.000Z","msg":"成班又係度分化屌前線<br />\n屌你老母企過上前線就知<br />\n無人迫你企 無人呃你留"},{"pid":"330ef602e1864e26314f15454aef2e291368de13","tid":1401821,"uid":199502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:17:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你有無搞錯？你語氣可唔可以好啲啊！？下？<br />\n積極鼓勵得唔得啊？</span>"},{"pid":"07a12b977d47067366cec37f9a9166cd3e14ed3b","tid":1401821,"uid":88428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:17:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家請珍惜前線<br />\n佢地付出最多</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0698c6656a079b93be081aeb0be67d1717a8b8fe","tid":1401821,"uid":37901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3fbce0033329294baa61ee9b8c0b46cdfd4f1683","tid":1401821,"uid":78186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:15:16.000Z","msg":"我見到都好撚嬲<br />\n大家一家要守撚住網軍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:17:56.000Z","msg":"一個ＰＯＳＴ屌前線無腦留守無目的，就幾千正評<br />\n成班睇住直播屌佢地無腦<br />\n連登不嬲都係三毛重地<br />\n人地日日等緊機會分化我地<br />\n<br />\n你睇下對家Ｄ人做柒野，人地係唔會重提架<br />\n前線可能戰略有錯，但係你地日提夜提，又無人真係上前線幫手，剩係屌有撚用咩"},{"pid":"6c6569a69ab60b9aaaacbabf873d11e1e7d4d2c8","tid":1401821,"uid":199502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"330ef602e1864e26314f15454aef2e291368de13","tid":1401821,"uid":199502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:17:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你有無搞錯？你語氣可唔可以好啲啊！？下？<br />\n積極鼓勵得唔得啊？</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:18:10.000Z","msg":"下次咁樣屌柒嗰啲分化撚。"},{"pid":"51ac6ca597809b19557e559595d92c3ea3cf7796","tid":1401821,"uid":37901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:27:05.000Z","msg":"咪撚唔記得１４年我地點輸<br />\n頂撚住班網軍啊"}]}